-- Spain to issue bonds maturing 2014, 2015 and 2017 October 4
-- 
-- Fri Sep 28, 2012 8:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/09/28/us-spain-bonds-idUSBRE88R0NZ20120928

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - Spain's Treasury said on Friday it would issue bonds maturing 2014, 2015 and 2017 at an auction on October 4. 
 The debt sale will include a bond maturing October 31, 2014, with a 3.3 percent coupon, a bond due October 31, 2015, with a 3.75 percent coupon and paper maturing July 30, 2017 with a 5.5 percent coupon. The target value of the issuance will be announced at around 1200 GMT on Monday. (Reporting By Paul Day; Editing by  Fiona Ortiz )